text: NRD could refer to: * Nidaros Roller Derby, Norway * Non-radiative dielectric, or non-radiating dielectric, as used in non-radiative dielectric waveguide * Noranda (mining company), Toronto Stock Exchange symbol NRD * Nordic Airways, ICAO airline code NRD * North Road railway station, National Rail station code NRD * Non-delivery report, Microsoft Exchange Server system message
title: NRD
